window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Crush your enemies and see them fall at their feet</b></p> <p>Faced with cavalry and horse archers alike, Matt Fang finds his armies out of position and reeling. He's going to have to pull back, concentrate his forces and pull off some miracle if he doesn't want to be a victim of his latest opponent.</p> <p>Good thing he's got new allies and even more units to play with. Now, all he needs is the time to get them in place.<br> <br> <i>Magic Kingdom at War</i> is a tactical, base-building, crunchy LitRPG novella series by Tao Wong, bestselling author of the <i>System Apocalypse, A Thousand Li, Climbing the Ranks, the Hidden Universe </i>and <i>Adventures on Brad</i> series.</p>"; 
